rows.label: qst006102_msg0001
rows.name:
This is no place for civilians.
This area is under military investigation.

rows.label: qst006102_msg0002
rows.name:
The stele is still being examined. We
can't have any civilians mucking about
with it. It might fall to bits!

rows.label: qst006102_msg0101
rows.name:
Oh, my... Are you a royal personage?!
Well, I'm sure you'd know how to
handle a fine thing like that...

rows.label: qst006102_msg0102
rows.name:
Please, examine it to your heart's
content, your Royalness!
